<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h2 class="h2-heading-ss w-100">
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        Benefits 
      </span>
       of authentication
    </h2>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width w-100">
      Authenticating a Saint Laurent bag provides several benefits, including:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-start">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Verification of authenticity:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         Authentication ensures that the bag is genuine and not counterfeit, providing confidence in the bag’s legitimacy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Increased value:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Authenticating a Saint Laurent bag can increase its value, as it provides proof of its legitimacy and authenticity, making it more desirable to potential buyers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Peace of mind:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Authentication provides peace of mind for fashion enthusiasts and collectors, ensuring that their investment is genuine and not counterfeit. This assurance allows them to enjoy their Saint Laurent bags with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

